<br>
I don't think that talking about the sustained DPS boost FB can provide is the right approach. SCM, SCF, MC and so on are the increases to long term DPS. FB is the increase to short term DPS, and it needs to be balanced as such. Good comparisons for what FB should do are Manaburn and melee offensive disciplines. <p><center>
